  "texts": [
    "Together, they establish a coherent context and lay a foundation for the following sections.",
    "Research ScopeBased on the surveys discussed in the previous section, we identify two independent taxonomies in the technical and artistic realms.",
    "The first taxonomy, typical in surveys with a technical focus, categorizes diffusion-based generative techniques as one of the generative methods and art as an application scenario [16,44,80,93].",
    "On the other hand, surveys with an artistic stance commonly adopt historical or theoretical perspectives, categorize relevant research by application scenarios and artistic categories (in Sec.",
    "5.1, we correspond them to different data modalities or applications), and focus more on the implications of generated results [17,36,89,90,168]."
  ],
